Metrics

Filtered columns by values

So i break data into different category

The SKU ID is unique within each country and each SKU is part of a “product”
group


Metrics

The SKU IDs follow a pattern of ABC-xx-xxxxx-x where the first 3 characters
denote the SKU

The PTN-10-31250-2 is part of the “PTN” category (Protein) Other categories
Included in the dataset: DAI (Dairy), PRO (processed food). All unit prices are
in local currency category













